docs {
  # Get Cleanup Rules
  
  Retrieves name cleanup rules used for normalizing merchant names.
  
  ## Response
  
  ```json
  {
    "success": true,
    "data": [
      {
        "id": 1,
        "pattern": "/\\d{6,}/gi",
        "replacement": "",
        "isActive": true
      }
    ]
  }
  ```
}
